<D>__{you didn't lose me. you rejected me.}
<C>__{charlie}
<D>__{i'm unrejecting you.}
<C>__{harriet}
<D>__{how do i know you won't reject me again?}
<C>__{charlie}
<D>__{i love you.}
<C>__{harriet}
<P>__{(after a long pause)}
<D>__{i love you. but you blew it, charlie, you blew it.}
<A>__{she goes into the house. charlie stands there dejected. he knows he's blown it.}
